s-of-1_47-misses-0_01-revenue-of-14_1b-misses-20m\">Q2 results</a>, which did not satisfy the investors, as the shares slumped over 8% on the market open. The demand for its cloud infrastructure and services is robust, and the pipeline is healthy. However, it</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743331-oracle-q2-great-cloud-performance-valuation-stretched", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 19:30:25"}, {"id": "4743321", "title": "CVS Health: When The Industry Is In Crisis, Don't Pick The Weaker Players", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"People shopping at CVS / pharmacy\" data-id=\"1166290360\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Sundry Photography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Many words have been written about the tough state of the health services sector in the years following the pandemic. Rising costs, higher utilization, regulatory scrutiny, price cuts, increased competition, a cyberattack, and now a shooting of one of the industry's leading CEOs, have all</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743321-cvs-health-when-the-industry-is-in-crisis-dont-pick-the-weaker-players", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 19:26:00"}, {"id": "4743317", "title": "Everus Construction Group Shows Strength In First Quarter Of Independence", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/463245227/image_463245227.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Caucasian workers in cherry pickers repairing power line\" data-id=\"463245227\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/463245227/image_463245227.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/463245227/image_463245227.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/463245227/image_463245227.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/463245227/image_463245227.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/463245227/image_463245227.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/463245227/image_463245227.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/463245227/image_463245227.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/463245227/image_463245227.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Ariel Skelley/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Everus Construction Group (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ECG\" title=\"Everus Construction Group, Inc.\">ECG</a></span>) had its first day of trading on November 1 of this year. The company was spun off from MDU Resources Group, Inc. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MDU\" title=\"MDU Resources Group, Inc.\">MDU</a>), a utility company I have</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/463245227/image_463245227.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743317-everus-construction-group-shows-strength-in-first-quarter-of-independence", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 19:20:50"}, {"id": "4743310", "title": "Covestro: Good Valuation Timing, Decent Upside, But Price Is High (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1427667582/image_1427667582.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Covestro buildings and plant, Antwerpen, Belgium\" data-id=\"1427667582\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1003px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1427667582/image_1427667582.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1427667582/image_1427667582.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1427667582/image_1427667582.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/