><p>5.76%</p></td> <td><p>13.72%</p></td> <td><p>5.22%</p></td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p><strong>Bloomberg US Aggregate</strong></p> <p><strong>Bond Index (Benchmark)</strong> </p> </td> </tr> </table> </span></span>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1975527024/image_1975527024.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743306-amundi-climate-transition-core-bond-fund-q3-2024-performance-and-market-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 19:02:00"}, {"id": "4743315", "title": "German Bunds Still Face Pressure Relative To Risk-Free Rates", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"German flag fluttering front of Reichstag building. Berlin, Germany\" data-id=\"1196974543\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5864px\" height=\"3909px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">arsenisspyros</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/benjamin-schroeder/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Benjamin Schroeder</a></em></p> <h2>The Bund spread remains under pressure, but we also see arguments for stabilisation</h2> <p>There had been a general sense that the central banks' quantitative tightening paired with ongoing high funding needs would require a reassessment of sovereign</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196974543/image_1196974543.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743315-german-bunds-face-pressure-relative-to-risk-free-rates", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 19:00:00"}, {"id": "4743301", "title": "XLK: Addressing The Unappealing Aspects", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Artificial intelligence circuit board 1\" data-id=\"1370479405\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1032px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Jonathan Kitchen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Technology Select Sector SPDR\u00ae Fund ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XLK\" title=\"The Technology Select Sector SPDR\u00ae Fund ETF\">XLK</a></span>) is the go-to fund for concentrated technology exposure. However, many find the concentration in its top three stocks unappealing, and XLK's simple methodology can lead to underperformance when individual industry groups are</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370479405/image_1370479405.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743301-xlk-etf-addressing-unappealing-aspects", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 18:48:09"}, {"id": "4743298", "title": "Magnolia Oil & Gas: Continued Improvements In Capital Efficiency", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151247502/image_2151247502.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oil pumps and wind mill during sunset.\" data-id=\"2151247502\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"947px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151247502/image_2151247502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151247502/image_2151247502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151247502/image_2151247502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151247502/image_2151247502.jpg?io=get